`CREATE` (https://web.archive.org/web/20230921103540/https://www.evm.codes/#f0?fork=shanghai) and `CREATE2`
(https://web.archive.org/web/20230921103540/https://www.evm.codes/#f5?fork=shanghai) EVM opcodes as well as of
